name: Lets hope the disease gets the better of him

metadata.name: Why did Huang Quan save the Chinese God of War?
metadata.description:
"Huangquan should have received money from the Chinese god of War, a lot of money!"



"I think Huangquan himself is the god of war in China, but it has been kept secret."



"People are too speculating. Huangquan killed the War god, probably because he wanted to kill people."



A flight to the magic of the passenger plane, passengers are discussing why huang Quan saved the Chinese god of War.



Only a handsome, gentle young man looked out of the window and said nothing all the while.



"Why do you think Huang Quan saved the Chinese God of War?"



"Asked the girl next to her.
